snippet.title: AVENGERS: DOOMSDAY (2026) | X-Men Trailer | Marvel Comics | Concept
snippet.description:
#Marvel #Avengers #Avengersdoomsday #ChrisEvans #Robertdowneyjr 
 
🎥 Attention viewers! (ITS FAN MADE)
The Avengers: Doomsday trailer teases the most dangerous chapter of the Marvel Cinematic Universe, setting up an epic clash in Avengers Doomsday (2026) as the MCU enters Phase 6. With Robert Downey Jr. rumored as Doctor Doom, the Avengers Doomsday teaser and Marvel trailer hint at a world-ending threat, massive battles, and a powerful new era shaped by Doctor Doom in the MCU. From shocking reveals to a stacked Avengers Doomsday cast, this movie promises to redefine the future of Marvel Studios, bringing comics-inspired chaos, multiversal stakes, and the ultimate test for Earth’s mightiest heroes.

The inspiration behind this video:
The moment we've been waiting for has finally arrived! In this video, we break down the explosive Avengers Doomsday trailer that just dropped online, confirming the shocking return of Chris Evans as Steve Rogers. While the Avengers Doomsday trailer official release gives us a glimpse of a retired Rogers, leaks of a second Avengers Doomsday teaser featuring Thor and the X-Men are breaking the internet. We analyze every frame of these reveals to understand how Marvel Studios is setting up the ultimate confrontation for Avengers 2026 . From the "Steve Rogers Will Return" title card to the first look at Robert Downey Jr Doctor Doom , we cover everything you need to know about the beginning of Marvel Phase 6 .

We dive deep into the massive Avengers Doomsday cast , which is shaping up to be the biggest ensemble in history. Beyond the Robert Downey Jr MCU comeback as the terrifying Doctor Doom MCU variant, we discuss the leaked footage of Cyclops and the X-Mansion that suggests a multiverse collision of epic proportions. We explore the theories that this Doctor Doom movie will see Victor Von Doom uniting the heroes before betraying them, and how Marvel is weaving storylines from the comics like Time Runs Out and Secret Wars into the Avengers Doomsday movie plot. Is Avengers Doctor Doom a hero, a villain, or something far more complex?

Finally, we look at the road ahead for the Marvel Cinematic Universe and MCU Phase 5 's conclusion. We provide a detailed breakdown of the Doomsday trailer easter eggs, including the connections to The Fantastic Four: First Steps and Avatar: Fire and Ash . Whether you are searching for Dr Doom trailer secrets or just want to see the community's reaction to the Avengers Doomsday hype, this video is your ultimate guide. Don't miss our predictions for who will survive the final battle and our full analysis of the Avengers Doomsday marvel trailer leaks.

I love you, please say

'Til the end of time

These three words

And I promise you that we will always be together
Oh, I love you
Please say you love me too
Please please
Say you love me too
'Til the end of time
My baby
Together, together, forever
'Til the end of time
I love you

Shining bright

Lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Going back to the corner where I first saw you
Gonna camp in my sleeping bag, I'm not gonna move
Got some words on cardboard, got your picture in my hand
Saying, "If you see this girl, can you tell her where I am?"
Some try to hand me money, they don't understand
I'm not broke, I'm just a broken-hearted man
I know it makes no sense, what else can I do?
And how can I move on when I'm still in love with you?

[Chorus]
'Cause if one day you wake up, and find that you're missing me
And your heart starts to wonder where on this Earth I could be
Thinking maybe you'll come back here to the place that we'd meet
And you'll see me waiting for you, on the corner of the street
So I'm not moving
I'm not moving

[Verse 2]
Policeman says, "Son, you can't stay here"
I say, "There's someone I'm waiting for
If it's a day, a month, a year"
Gotta stand my ground, even if it rains or snows
If she changes her mind, this is the first place she will go

[Chorus]
'Cause if one day you wake up, and find that you're missing me
And your heart starts to wonder where on this Earth I could be
Thinking maybe you'll come back here to the place that we'd meet
And you'll see me waiting for you, on the corner of the street
So I'm not moving
I'm not moving
I'm not moving
I'm not moving

[Bridge]
People talk about the guy who's waiting on a girl, oh
There are no holes in his shoes, but a big hole in his world, mmm
Maybe I'll get famous as the man who can't be moved
And maybe you won't mean to, but you'll see me on the news

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

I'm down on bended knee

Can we go back to the days our love was strong?

Oh, God, give me the reason
I'm down on bended knee

I'm down on bended knee

Say I'm sorry

The blame is on me

Come home

Wanna build a new life
Can you tell me how a perfect love goes wrong?
Just you and me
Gonna make you my wife
Raise a family
Can somebody tell me how to get things back the way they used to be?
Oh, God, give me the reason
I'm down on bended knee

I'll never walk again 'til you come back to me
I'm down on bended knees
